{"tid":686560,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"巴士大大聲講野","createTime":"2018-06-01T11:33:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-01T12:32:54.000Z","uid":11539,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8bfbd5026bde7b4d513737dfb02a14246fae993d","tid":686560,"uid":11539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T11:33:30.000Z","msg":"搭機場巴士<br />\n我就唔係好攰嘅<br />\n咁後面有一家人（兩公婆加兩個18-22仔）<br />\n喺度大大聲傾計<br />\n我聽咗十幾分鐘<br />\n忍唔住話「唔好意思，可唔可以細聲少少」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地即刻話「吓？未聽過香港巴士唔講得野喎」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大佬呀，叫你地靜啲唔係叫你地唔好講野呀<br />\n仲要大大聲繼續話咩巴士唔講得野呀嗰啲說話<br />\n成家人都咁幼稚起曬鋼咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主講得啱<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主唔忍得，嗰家人係啱嘅"},{"pid":"d9a8e12e3c8f76df8c33e93a33332de4ee2b0dee","tid":686560,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T11:34:23.000Z","msg":"紅忍咁唔忍得 渣"},{"pid":"c4f98d72ee33b1a3cb2d6dee6f75e81bd4a86ced","tid":686560,"uid":11539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9a8e12e3c8f76df8c33e93a33332de4ee2b0dee","tid":686560,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T11:34:23.000Z","msg":"紅忍咁唔忍得 渣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T11:38:17.000Z","msg":"唔通我真係唔應該叫佢地細聲少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba8a6315a06e9640b009ebef993a13784b682b7","tid":686560,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T11:59:11.000Z","msg":"啲自我中心嘅仆街係咁架啦，放工時間成車都靜靜休息打機聽歌煲劇，啲仆街就嘈撚著曬"},{"pid":"cd48c6d10462b387ed077419d9f728b684b989a7","tid":686560,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T12:07:55.000Z","msg":"即刻落車"},{"pid":"44bd896e32290f99266be8dc36e71b3cdfb40053","tid":686560,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4f98d72ee33b1a3cb2d6dee6f75e81bd4